    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-vv40-lead-assessor",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped as not-assessed consistent with MRL 2 requirements for a Class II CPB device. The CFD hemolysis model is accepted as sufficiently credible to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions within the scope described in the simulation plan. This model has been applied in clinical research contexts and the evidence base supports the Accepted decision at MRL 2.",
